name: Sars Covid 2 / Jarjar Variant
description:
NFT created from @Bayneko1's Sars Covid 2 project that was dropped on multiple HEN wallets on 02/02/22.
This variant presents multiple genomic mutations that increase its transmissibility and severity, and it rendering most vaccines ineffective. Please maintain biosecurity measures and remember to wear your mask before purchasing this NFT.
It was made with Processing 4.0 and exporting in video format with Movie Maker.
This NFT uses the sounds: cue1-hospital.mp3 and operationroominspace.wav from users plantmom_elise and antwerpsounddesign of Freesound platform. It is used under a Creative Common CCO 1.0 license, which you can consult here: https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/
